listing_company_name: Colac to Coast Real Estate - Colac
description:
Don't miss this exciting opportunity to purchase one of four generously sized allotments securing your place in a thriving community just ten minutes from Colac. 'Coragulac Acres' is situated within close proximity to Red Rock Scenic Lookout, St Brendan's Catholic Primary School, Coragulac Kindergarten, Red Rock Winery and St Andrews Anglican Church.

Each allotment offers the chance to spread out and embrace the space to watch your family grow, keep a pony or pursue hobby farming. From one acre to 14 acres there is a block for you! With town water, power to pit, titles granted and offering stunning views from each allotment, don't miss out on an enviable lifestyle.

Additional features you will love:

- Colac town garbage collection service
- RSD mail service
- Secondary School bus stop only 700 metres away!
- $1,000 vouchers will be gifted for the Warrion Cottage Nursery and Cororooke General Store and Post Office for each block purchased!

Contact Exclusive selling agents Colac to Coast Real Estate on 5231 3288 for more information.
